Engineering Innovation Robot Control
Copyright 2026 Tian Bingzhuo and project contributors

This repository documents a team engineering-innovation competition project.
The award and engineering result were completed collaboratively.

Known contribution split:

- Wang Shuo and Zhang Jiayu: mechanical structure fabrication and mechanism
  bring-up.
- Su Yuxuan: vision/perception code, including camera and OpenCV recognition
  logic.
- Tian Bingzhuo: all non-vision software work, including Raspberry Pi main
  control flow, GPIO/I2C/serial interfaces, actuator logic, manual/automatic
  control modes, integration debugging, and public repository maintenance.

During the original competition period, part of the non-vision software was
drafted or debugged with assistance from the then-available ChatGPT. Codex was
not available at that time and was not part of the original competition
development.

